# Branding Agency Nepal: Why Branding Matters for Businesses  

Many businesses in Nepal focus heavily on sales and promotions but overlook one critical foundation: **branding**.

Branding is not just about logos or colors. It defines how customers perceive your business, how much they trust you, and whether they choose you over competitors. This is why working with a professional **branding agency in Nepal** is becoming essential for long-term business growth.

