## What Branding Really Means  

Branding is the complete identity of your business. It includes:

- Brand name and positioning  
- Visual identity (logo, colors, typography)  
- Brand voice and messaging  
- Customer experience  
- Market perception  

A strong brand communicates value instantly, even before a customer interacts with your product or service.

The best branding company in Nepal focuses on building clarity, consistency, and credibility across all customer touchpoints.

