## Branding vs Marketing: Understanding the Difference  

| Aspect | Branding | Marketing |
|------|---------|----------|
| Purpose | Build identity and trust | Promote products and services |
| Timeline | Long-term | Short to mid-term |
| Focus | Perception and positioning | Traffic and conversions |
| Impact | Emotional connection | Immediate action |

Marketing brings customers in. Branding makes them stay.

